                      boolean scaleWithDPI)
Constructs a BillboardStyle object from various parameters. Instantiating the object directly is
not recommended, BillboardStyleBuilder should be used instead.

Parameters:
color - The color for the billboard.
attachAnchorPointX - The horizontal attaching anchor point for the billboard.
attachAnchorPointY - The vertical attaching anchor point for the billboard.
causesOverlap - The causes overlap flag for the billboard.
hideIfOverlapped - The hide if overlapped flag for the billboard.
horizontalOffset - The horizontal offset for the billboard.
verticalOffset - The vertical offset for the billboard.
placementPriority - The placement priority for the billboard.
